title: BTS Talk 'Butter,' Tour Dates, Their McDonald's Meal & More
author: SiriusXM
description:
BTS stop by Hits1 to discuss their new song 'Butter', when they'll be returning to tour and their Billboard Music Award nominations, including "Top Selling Song" for 'Dynamite'.
